TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Pre SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: DELETE FROM IN_ST_CMTX WHERE TXT_FILE_NAME='$$STR_CONTROL_FILE_NAME'; COMMIT;

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
UPDATE IN_ETL_CONTROL SET TXT_KEY_VALUE=(SELECT LPAD(TO_CHAR(COUNT(*)),10,'0') FROM IN_ST_CMTX WHERE TXT_FILE_NAME='$$STR_CONTROL_FILE_NAME'), DTE_UPDATE_DATE=SYSDATE WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING='CMTX_PRESTAGE_RECORD_COUNT' AND TXT_FILE_NAME='$$STR_CONTROL_FILE_NAME';
COMMIT;
